  "note": "Operator 2026-07-20 ('horiz divider needed', screenshot of the song canvas): the stacked section cards ran straight into the add-a-section template area below with no visual break. A labeled horizontal divider (#songCanvasDiv, 'Add a section') separates 'your song so far' from 'add the next section' - the app's own group-boundary grammar (same rationale as the in-key barrier, decisions.md). Shows only on the canvas WITH sections above it (nothing to divide on an empty canvas). Red-first on 6b7044a.",
